TextEng: Go ahead, though I doubt it shall do any good.
Text: 해 보시지. 별 소용은 없을 것 같지만.

TextEng: Farewell for now.
Have your blessings had an effect on the progress of the plague?
Text: 당신들의 축복이 역병의 진행에 효과가 있었나?

TextEng: Where is the Great Graveyard?
Will people be safe if I bring them here?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is this the only haven? People could fortify elsewhere.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 여기가 유일한 피난처인가? 다른 곳도 방비할 수 있을 텐데.

TextEng: Do you know who is creating the zombies?
I welcome the offer, thank you.
You will forgive me if I do not indulge, thank you.
I am not interested in your hollow blessings.
Text: 그 비어 있는 축복에는 관심 없어.

TextEng: No thanks. No blessing wanted.
Give me blessing if you want. Probably do nothing.
Text: 축복 줄 거면 줘. 아마 아무 소용 없어.

TextEng: No want. Take a hike.
Sure. Give me blessing. Thanks much.
Bye now.
Blessings slow plague down yet?
People be safe if me bring here?
Uh, you know who make plague zombies?
Text: 어, 역병 좀비 만든 놈 알아?

TextEng: Where am this Great Graveyard thingy?
Can you offer basic temple services?
Text: 기본적인 사원 서비스를 제공할 수 있나?

TextEng: Maybe you gots store of basic temple stuff?
Text: 사원 기본 물건 파는 가게 있나?
